      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEET SWEET TOOTH (1) was responsible for a far better performance last start, finishing second over 1720m at Penrith. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Meets a comparable field so she can add to the sound recent effort. RONZEL SONNY (7) finished third at Dubbo two starts back then did a great job again at his latest appearance over 1660m at at this track, beaten 3.5 metres into third after being close to the pace throughout. Drawn to enjoy a cosy run but might need things to go his way at some stage. Meets a similar line up and he can figure in the finish. COUNTRY MAJOR (6) is in the mix following a sixth at his most recent appearance over 1609m at Tamworth. REASON TO PARTY (8) is the best of the rest after finishing sixth over 1660m at this track last time out.",
